@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title package-manager 远端 MCP 部署视图

node "Local PC" {
  [opencode\nmodel: alibaba-cn/glm-5] as OpenCode
  [Skill\npackage-manager-install-guarded] as Skill
}

cloud "Network" {
  [HTTP(S) /mcp] as Net
}

node "Remote Host / Container" {
  [package_manager.mcp_server\n(FastMCP streamable-http)] as MCP
  [Auth Layer\nStatic Token / HMAC Token\nScope: pm:read, pm:write] as Auth
  [control_plane.py\nwhitelist tools] as CP
  [install lock\n.mcp_install.lock] as Lock
  [package-manager binary] as Bin
  database "install_state\n.package-manager/.install_state.yaml" as State
  database "config/packages.yaml" as Cfg
}

OpenCode --> Skill : 自然语言触发
Skill --> OpenCode : 生成工具调用计划
OpenCode --> Net : call pm_* tools
Net --> MCP
MCP --> Auth : verify token + scopes
Auth --> CP : allow/reject
CP --> Cfg : read runtime config
CP --> Lock : acquire/release
CP --> Bin : run --name/--dry-run
Bin --> State : update install state
CP --> MCP : structured result
MCP --> OpenCode : tool response

@enduml
